text.tspan: Ever since I could hold a pencil, creative endevours have
always been my biggest passion. Creating, designing, and
making things beautiful is one side of the coin, while my
more analytical side loves the idea of sorting information
and making things easier to do.
I am a designer who simply enjoys making people happy.
I'm not shy to try new things that can be challenging--from
coding to videography, and anything inbetween! On my
spare time, you can find me drawing, playing video games,
fan-girling over pens or listening to educational podcasts.
